Left press one corner, release on the opposite corner. A square will be selected to zoom into. Note the word square
Also note that a click will zoom out
Scroll changes detail
Right click results in the menu. Suggestion is to press space to disable rendering before entering the menu
Middle click changes to a the Julia Set of the point clicked

Suggested parameters: +RTS -N -qb -qg -g1

Input Syntax
Complex numbers are specified as real+imag
Polynomials are specified as a comma seperated list of complex numbers which are interpreted as coefficients to their respective indices
